description:
Taichi Nakanishi is now available as a new playable character in Captain Tsubasa: Rise of New Champions.

A giant goalie & the captain of Naniwa MS.
He was invited to the Junior Hero League for his performance & skill as he has participated in the Nationals for two years in a row.
As well as power reflecting his physique, he defends the goal utilizing surprisingly high agility.
name: Captain Tsubasa: Rise of New Champions - Taichi Nakanishi
